Previous work

Before learning to code, my profession was teaching! You might ask, "what did you teach?"
The answer to that is a little complicated.

Subject Grades Years taught Class Style Class Size
Highschool Math 9th through 12th 3 Years In-person 2 to 8 students
Science 7th through 12th 3 Years In-person 2 to 8 students
Test Prep 7th through 12th 2 Years Virtual 1 to 6 students
Elementary Math 2nd through 6th 5 Years Virtual 1 to 5 students
Various Tutoring 7th through College 8 Years In-person and Virtual Usually 1-on-1

As you can see, I've spent several years teaching across many different subjects and age groups.
I haven't even included everything!
I pride myself on being adaptable and a quick study. Several of the subects I've taught I was definitely not qualified to teach.
If I don't know something, that just means I get to learn!
